{"tid":446033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳橋男高呼「阿Sa我愛你」","createTime":"2017-10-24T02:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T10:00:45.000Z","uid":23189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99eace45e88e5cc357351f2d00f7007b769638d0","tid":446033,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171024/20192565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171024%2F20192565&d=KHW6nftp2oq6oQc8USE1UwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5e65c668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171024%2F20192565&h=074389c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171024/20192565</a><br />\n<br />\n一名癡情丈夫聲稱為證明很愛妻子，昨早攀上東鐵大埔墟站出口一隧道口簷篷頂，大叫老婆名字及「我愛你」後一躍而下，結果墮至5米下地面受傷，途人發現報警。事主送院治理後情況嚴重，警方事後聯絡其妻了解，案件暫列企圖自殺處理。<br />\n疑為情「跳橋」姓陳男子（41歲）任職運輸工，與姓梁妻子報稱住石硤尾大坑東邨。消息稱，夫婦近日因感情問題爭執。昨早9時許，陳突走至大埔墟站A出口對開，攀上隧道頂部簷篷後高呼其妻姓名：「阿Sa（其妻名字），我愛你！」隨後一躍而下墮至5米下地面，身體多處受傷，有途人發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n近日與妻因家事鬧翻<br />\n男事主清醒送往大埔那打素醫院，經治理後情況嚴重。警方聯絡其妻了解，得悉陳近日因感情及家事與妻鬧翻，為證明自己很愛妻子「連死都願意」，故「跳橋」以示決心。警方指事件無可疑，列企圖自殺案處理。"},{"pid":"6d3b2c1314970abbc806c285d2c3243b79502800","tid":446033,"uid":70985,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/10/101.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101016103517\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F10%2F101.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101016103517&h=b3cc6635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbf548ac42f0aee6acb7dac04fff283ad1e8ae11","tid":446033,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲都咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66f6b7b2313e19fdb6bcf4e43b26ec84d7ec2a9","tid":446033,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"有冇叫人錄低比老婆睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7258cf291d520d1dece6143df31666266e2678af","tid":446033,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"係咪叫雞俾老婆發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c1eab36a4106e4947158ad2037dc33c7443018","tid":446033,"uid":137729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a48c57c0ac39fd3b82b41e8423db59d2794d80","tid":446033,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/79189_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F79189_WM.jpg&h=723b2d47&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}